All of my failures in this trial have been due to early casting resulting in a dead cleric/chanter or shaman.  I haven't tried it again since I got AE taunt, but I think I will do soon.<br>
It may be that this trial is not possible with a medium weight tank like myself (just over 4k hp unbuffed) - the mobs hit significantly harder than the exec mobs, so the cleric can't keep up with his low aggro heal over time spells and ends up dieing when he tries a fill-in heal.  Most of the mobs in this trial cannot be rooted and are immune to snare (as I found out when I tried it with my druid instead).<br>
